{"tid":1876860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子疑打爛車窗偷8盒N95被捕","createTime":"2020-02-12T16:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T16:49:12.000Z","uid":207197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"412df84005ae961d376fcfaa3df0eddfd585ed3c","tid":1876860,"uid":207197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"市面口罩供應緊張，炒價高達幾十元一個，衍生不少罪案。警方昨日接獲一名53歲姓廖男子報案，指其停泊在上水新成路的私家車車窗有損毀，車內有八盒共一百六十個N95口罩不見了，懷疑被人盜去。<br />\n大埔警區刑事調查隊第九隊人員經進一步調查後，今日凌晨約3時45分在上水彩園邨拘捕一名三十三歲姓梁男子，涉嫌車內盜竊被捕。警方不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n警方提醒市民要小心保管財物，包括口罩或其他個人防護用品，以免被賊人有機可乘。"},{"pid":"7d61b0e2e0f9c60586bbc90b77e66fe7d30802ff","tid":1876860,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"政府無能，迫到香港人要偷口罩"},{"pid":"a55c3fedcbafce83d47cdc04364ab2e1f798baa5","tid":1876860,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"N95 160個咁重貨. <br />\n<br />\n而家N95係香港值錢過黃金.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852d121a689d82f7fadf0af9bc4de84901c4a6ac","tid":1876860,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:22:17.000Z","msg":"死炒狗， 鬼唔望你中廢炎"},{"pid":"fe8ada5f162a12c684db66ffb9d9d463d36b137e","tid":1876860,"uid":271513,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"咁又真係抵拉喎<br />\n<br />\n成八盒咁多！"},{"pid":"165d50977d13ddbcb59b2ffa25662c7a87bbd038","tid":1876860,"uid":311034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"無能嘅政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前省港奇兵嚟香港係搶錢搶金條 屌你老母依家落嚟喺搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  7婆仲要中門大開 爭未撚開記招歡迎支那人落嚟搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa09a1eb949746d0d4d5c789089d